title: Grateful Dead Live at Charlotte Coliseum on 1989-10-22
description:
Set 1

Foolish Heart, Minglewood Blues, Mississippi Half Step, Queen Jane Approximately, Ramble On Rose, Beat It On Down The Line, Bird Song, Johnny B. Goode

Set 2

Blow Away, Samson & Delilah, Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Black Muddy River
